sequenceDiagram
    participant App as App Code
    participant Core as SwiftIntelligenceCore
    participant Module as Capability Module
    participant Cache as Module Cache
    participant Apple as Apple Framework
    participant Result as Typed Result

    App->>Core: configure(with:)
    App->>Module: request operation
    Module->>Cache: lookup
    alt cache hit
        Cache-->>Module: cached value
        Module-->>App: typed result
    else cache miss
        Module->>Apple: native framework call
        Apple-->>Module: raw output
        Module->>Module: post-process / normalize
        Module->>Cache: store result
        Module-->>Result: typed output
        Result-->>App: final value
    end

    Note over App,Result: Long-lived engines such as VisionEngine may require explicit initialize() and shutdown().
